item.title: CVE-2019-10215|2024-08-04T22:17:18.875Z -- red%20hat -- bootstrap3-typeahead.js
item.description: Bootstrap-3-Typeahead after version 4.0.2 is vulnerable to a cross-site scripting flaw in the highlighter() function. An attacker could exploit this via user interaction to execute code in the user's browser.
